Heroes of Cosplay - Season 1, Episode 3





MegaCon

Next stop on the Victoria And Jinyo Should Break Up Tour is MegaCon, a fifty-thousand-strong convention in Orlando, FL. Yaya Han can't make it -- she's too busy becoming an action figure, which involves striking a pose in a green-screen-type pedestal contraption in order to become a video game version of herself.




Original Air Date: 27-Aug-2013
